Class MORDescriptor.ReadingOutcome

    MORDescriptor

    public class MORDescriptor.ReadingOutcome
extends Semantics.ReadingOutcome<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLLiteral>
    A container for reading results.

    It implements an extension of Semantics.ReadingOutcome by specifying the type of the reading buffer as OWLLiteral.
